IMPORTANT INTERVIEW / EXAM QUESTIONS

Q. CPU ka function kya hai?
Ans. Instructions execute karta hai aur processing karta hai.

Q. RAM volatile memory kyun kehlati hai?
Ans. Power off hone par data erase ho jata hai.

Q. POST ka full form?
Ans. Power-On Self Test.

Q. UEFI ka purpose?
Ans. Hardware initialize karna aur Operating System boot karna.

Q. Bootloader kya karta hai?
Ans. Operating System ko RAM me load karta hai aur control OS ko de deta hai.

Q. Motherboard ka main role?
Ans. Sabhi hardware components ko connect aur communicate karwana.
